thread.title_full: Ingram's Water & Air Equipment reviewed by Mrs Y Brookes

author: Mrs Y Brookes
title: Mrs Y Brookes
text: Ingram's Water and Air Equipment DIY Mr Cool air con/heat unit was easy for me to install and the unit is very quiet to run, very efficient to run and, I feel, very good value for money. Ingram's seem to be a very reputable company.
